assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍子其實都係樂理嘅一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你見其他樂器都需要拍子感就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只不過你識唔識練習嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等同於如果個俾份五線譜你你可唔可以跟住佢數返個拍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要你識分呢一啲野其實就會識數拍子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最簡單嘅係你數唔數得出一首歌嘅重拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如你可唔可以聽住首歌數到1234<br />\n音準問題其實都係可以訓練返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如依家就好多apps,你唱緊一粒音嗰陣佢就可以顯示返你唱緊嘅音準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於唱歌點樣先可以唔傷到喉嚨,呢樣野我諗係每一個唱歌導師都會教嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16406f215b2381e8a3415c066a9e17bdee7623ab","tid":1025980,"uid":173748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5284c0b5b1df2c4ad2c205060ea4be6411b16a27","tid":1025980,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"唱歌天生既<br />\n把聲靚 冇技巧都可以好好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"你咁講都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係同做運動一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有天份嘅人係會好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係永遠到最後努力嘅人都係會超越有天份嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然除非你係努力嘅天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f24ded2a968c0af8efe87b5ac4e60a4137f16e","tid":1025980,"uid":173748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Vocaljj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FVocaljj&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=e79576eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Vocaljj</a><br />\n有興趣可以tg交流吓<img sr